<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT3">
<l>pāliṟ kiṭantatuvum paṇṭaraka mēyatuvu</l>
<l>māliṟ ṟuyiṉṟatuvu māraṟivār ñālat</l>
<l>toruporuḷai vāṉavarta meypporuḷai yappi</l>
<l>laruporuḷai yāṉaṟinta vāṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will know [His] reclining on the milk, [His] dwelling in Raṅgam of old,</l>
<l>[His] sleeping on the banyan[-leaf], the world’s unique Essential Principle,</l>
<l>the celestials’ true Essence, the rare Meaning [lying on the] water</l>
<l>the way I have known [Him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
